Needs:
Germany Schaefer
Donnie Bush
Charlie Oleary
Sam Crawford
George Mullin
Hughie Jennings.
Toledo: Freeman, Abbott

not picky on stance or card, but looking for graded SGC or PSA no lower than 2.5. Also willing to purchase straight out and sell these if their is interest.
PM me if interested.
